eliability&quot; Live Online Electricity Today T&D Magazine Forum on January 31, 2023" /></li><li><img class="amazingsliderthumbnailimg" src="https://www.electricity-today.com/wp-content/uploads/COMMONWEALTH-PRESENTATION-150x150.jpg" alt="A Deep Dive into BESS Arc Flash" title="Ian Hutt, P.E. PMP, Project Manager, Commonwealth Associates Inc., presenting at the &quot;Electrical Power Reliability&quot; Live Online Electricity Today T&D Magazine Forum on January 31, 2023" /></li><li><img class="amazingsliderthumbnailimg" src="https://www.electricity-today.com/wp-content/uploads/IRISS-Presentation-MR-Jody-AA-150x150.jpg" alt="Improving Your Maintenance Program Through Operator-Driven Reliability" title="Jody Dado, Business Development Manager - Northwest US & Canada, IRISS Group, presenting at the &quot;Electrical Power Reliability&quot; Live Online Electricity Today T&D Magazine Forum on January 31, 2023" /></li><li><img class="amazingsliderthumbnailimg" src="https://www.electricity-today.com/wp-content/uploads/Zensol_31Jan2023_presentation-150x150.jpg" alt="Vibro-Acoustic as a Fast Diagnostic Tool for On Load Tap Changers" title="Dr. Fouad Brikci, President, Zensol Automation, Inc. presenting at the" /></li><li><img class="amazingsliderthumbnailimg" src="https://www.electricity-today.com/wp-content/uploads/MSAT-RoIP-solutions-1-150x150.jpg" alt="Mission Critical Communications for Lineman Safety and Security" title="Steve Hailey, Push to Talk Product Director, Network Innovation EN Inc., presenting at the &quot;Linemen Safety&quot; ET T&D Magazine Live Online Forum on November 22, 2022" /></li><li><img class="amazingsliderthumbnailimg" src="https://www.electricity-today.com/wp-content/uploads/Valard-Presentation-1-150x150.jpg" alt="How to Develop a Competency Program" title="Erinn Jacula, Training and Development Specialist and Shilo Neveu, Executive VP, Health & Safety, Valard Construction, presenting at the &quot;Linemen Safety&quot; ET T&D Magazine Live Online For